{
  "stem": "304.1",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to go with your children-- it was-- it was too-- too difficult, or almost impossible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to go to another country with papers officially, very few people were very lucky enough to get those papers and to-- to do it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember only one family who left from Chust to other places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were home till 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In 1944, March, one day we woke up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germany occupied all of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the real trouble started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the things that we survivors-- it's very, very typical when people used to ask us, and it happened to me a few  weeks again-- a few weeks ago again-- when they used to ask, why didn't you resist?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- they asked me personally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't ask my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They asked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was a child at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very hard to explain why we didn't resist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did resist, first of all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, I always see today what's going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I believe the best example is the hostages in Iran.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That the whole United States, with the mighty army behind them and they couldn't do too much.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they ask a Jewish girl survivor from Hitler's death camp from Auschwitz why didn't I survive-- why didn't I resist.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
